# Packetbeat

This image runs Packetbeat.

# Usage:

- Running ${IMAGE} binding the elasticsearch container.
  docker run -d --name ${IMAGE} -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock --link [elasticsearch-container]:elasticsearch ${REGISTRY}/${NAMESPACE}/${IMAGE}:${TAG}

- Running ${IMAGE} providing the DNS entry for elasticsearch.
  docker run -d --name ${IMAGE} -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -e ELASTICSEARCH_HOST=el.example.com ${REGISTRY}/${NAMESPACE}/${IMAGE}:${TAG}
